  <header class="stripe">
    <h1>Replacement Laptop Parts</h1>
    <div class="img-shadow left"><%= image_tag("shadow-left.png") %></div>
    <div class="img-shadow right"><%= image_tag("shadow-right.png") %></div>
  </header>
  <div  id="main-content">
    <div class="service">
      <p>
        More often than not when we have a laptop or computer, over a long period of time, wear and tear commonly takes place. Or we can sometimes be a bit clumsy and accidently scratch, break or smash parts. This is where Cheaper Computer Care comes in. With our specialist connections and expertise we will guarantee you the best replacement parts at the most cost effective prices.
      </p>
      <p>
        So if your computer screen is cracked, if your keyboard has keys no longer working, or any other problems then answer a few simple questions for a <b>no obligation</b> quote today. 
      </p>
      
      <% service = Service.where("lower(name) = 'replacement parts'").first %>
      <% if service %>
        <% if service.can_checkout %>
          <a href="<%= new_order_path('service' => service.id) %>" class="btn btn-large btn-success">Click here to get started</a>
        <% else %>
          <a href="<%= quote_service_path(service.id) %>" class="btn btn-large btn-success">Click here to get started</a>
        <% end %>
      <% else %>
        <a href="<%= new_order_path %>" class="btn btn-large btn-success">Click here to get started</a>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
